<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Diversity & Inclusion - ShaktiRide</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .hero img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffccd5, #ffb3c6);
      padding: 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-column {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 150px;
      margin: 10px;
    }

    .footer h5 {
      color: #4a0e3f;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #4a0e3f;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
      color: #d63384;
    }

    .sign-up {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffccd5, #ffb3c6);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .sign-up p {
      color: #4a0e3f;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .sign-up button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #d63384;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .sign-up button:hover {
      background-color: #ad1457;
    }

    /* Extra Footer Styling */
    .footer-extra {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffccd5, #ffb3c6);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e91e63;
    }

    .social-icons {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .social-icons a {
      color: #4a0e3f;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .social-icons a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.2);
      color: #d63384;
    }

    .app-buttons {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .app-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #d63384;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 0 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .app-btn i {
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    .app-btn:hover {
      background-color: #ad1457;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a0e3f;
    }

    .footer-bottom a {
      color: #4a0e3f;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 8px;
    }

    .footer-bottom a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
      color: #d63384;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Navbar -->
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-warning">
  <div class="container">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Shaktiride</a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
      <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/diversity">Diversity</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/sustainability">Sustainability</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero">
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529333166437-7750a6dd5a70?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" alt="Diversity">
</section>

<!-- Content -->
<div class="container my-5">
  <h1 class="mb-4">Diversity & Inclusion at ShaktiRide</h1>
  <p>At shaktiride, we believe in empowering women and creating a safe, inclusive environment for both passengers and drivers. Our female-only ride-hailing service promotes equality, celebrates diversity, and ensures that every woman feels confident when traveling.</p>
  <p>We are committed to building a platform where women from different backgrounds, cultures, and communities come together to support one another. Whether it’s through employment opportunities, training programs, or community engagement, we make sure diversity is at the heart of our mission.</p>
  <h3 class="mt-4">Our Key Initiatives</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Hiring women drivers from diverse backgrounds</li>
    <li>Providing equal pay and growth opportunities</li>
    <li>Hosting workshops to promote awareness</li>
    <li>Creating partnerships with women-led organizations</li>
  </ul>
</div>

